exceptions

class - 6xx

601 - Class not found
602 - Invalid class payload

user - 7xx

701 - User not found
702 - User personal data must be provided
703 - User already exists with provided e-mail
704 - User must have a valid address to be updated
705 - Invalid email or password
706 - E-mail or password not provided

address - 8xx

801 - Address not found
802 - Invalid address payload

schema - 901 - 998

901 - Verify the fields

unknown - 999

discipline - 10xx

1001 - Discipline not found
1002 - Discipline already exists

class-stage - 11xx

1101 - Class stage not found
1102 - Class stage already exists

auth - 12xx

1201 - Invaid token provided
1202 - A token must me provided

schedule - 13xx
1301 - This schedule already exists
1302 - Schedule not found